text: Irma Walther (14 September 1920 - 31 May 2005) was a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:2005 deaths Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nuremberg
